<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Hi everyone, i reach you in a sullen state right now. For my account is being canceled on april 15, 2001, because my father will no longer permit me to use his credit card (because he hates everquest because i play it so much and he'll do anything to get me to stop).<p>

I am only 17 years of age, so in no way shape or form can i own a regular credit card. I am hoping someone will read this who has had my same problem and can help me out. I am in the prime of my everquest experience, and it will kill me to stop, and i know some of you can relate! <p>

SO PLEASE PLEASE! if you have ANY information that could help me pay for everquest, PLEEASE post it here! i don't want to stop playing everquest! i have been playing since december, and it will kill me to stop! i really need your help, THANKS!</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
