<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Heh, I am having almost the exact same problem you are, but I'm going to get it back in a matter of days. My mom's work paid for her yearly fee for her card and when she took a medical leave of absence, they quit paying it. I was also threatned to leave EQ for good, but I talked her into letting me play on. The only thing I can suggest is to build up your faction with your dad and then spring the "Can I still keep EQ if I play less" question. Worked for me, it should work for you. Hope this helps.<hr>Shandria Swiftblade on Rodcet playing my Warrior, and, god, I love her!!</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
